data.description: Charming 4 bedroom Craftsman home with top of the hill views, owned-solar, and income from the ADU! Live in one, rent the other! Coming home to comfort is easier than ever when you have a brand new heating and A/C system. Enjoy the ambiance of the spacious living room with the wood burning stove. The open flow kitchen concept that opens to the large composite deck enables you to entertain guests while enjoying those wonderful views. The en suite master bedroom is conveniently adjacent to the living room and indoor laundry room. This home boasts a lot of new: Newer windows, newer septic system, and the entire living area, including the ADU, has been improved with a new Heating and Air Conditioning unit with multiple mini splits throughout. Say goodbye to utility bills and hello to energy independence with your owned-solar electric system. The studio rental offers private parking, a full kitchen, new flooring, a private backyard patio and is very easy to rent. Plenty of space for an RV parking on the large lot. This is a great opportunity to own a home that offers so much. Call your Realtor and see it today!
